posting_body: ['Pike Motorworks Apartments', '715 E Pine St, Seattle, WA, 98122', 'Interested in more information?', 'Visit link below:', '<URL>', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 2', 'OR Text', '2', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team.', 'Live at the Intersection of Classic Seattle and Right', 'Now', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 648 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Meet Pike Motorworks, the next chapter of the Pike/Pine renaissance, offering über-luxurious apartments and unrivaled amenities.', 'Every detail has been designed to preserve the site’s historic origins and celebrate The Hill’s effortless individuality, from the urban art sculpture in the courtyard to the building’s original 1926 auto row façade.', 'This is your chance to live at the intersection of classic Seattle and right now.', 'Features', '- Spacious floor plans', '- Spacious walk-in tiled showers*', '- Reclaimed wood doors', '- Premium hardware, fixtures and finishes throughout', '- Gourmet kitchens with striking custom cabinets', '- Grand vaulted ceilings', '- Extra-large custom closets', '- Wood-style plank flooring', '- Expansive insulated windows', '- Quartz counter-tops', '- Under-cabinet dimmable LED kitchen lighting', '- Energy-efficient GE stainless steel appliances', '- Abundant natural light', '- Stunning black ceramic tile back-splashes', '*Select Units', 'Community Amenities', '- Original repurposed materials', '- RPM fitness center', '- Station lounge', '- Pet decks', '- Urban art sculpture', '- Sunroof deck', '- Paw wash station', '- Accelerate business center', '- Vibrant retail courtyard', '- Redhook Brewpub', 'Office Hours', 'Monday-Sunday:9:00AM-6:00PM', 'Pet Policy', 'Pet friendly!', 'Please contact us for details.', 'We do not accept Comprehensive Reusable Tenant Screening Reports as defined by and pursuant to RCW 59.18.', 'Qq16HGsbt']
